OL,3,CNetwork Rail fined #3.75m over rail
OL,4,Cworker deaths
OL,6,FNetwork Rail has been fined #3.75m and
OL,7,Fordered to pay costs of #175,000 after
OL,8,Fpleading guilty to a breach of
OL,9,Fworkplace health and safety following
OL,10,Fthe death of two railway workers.
OL,12,FGareth Delbridge and Michael Lewis
OL,13,Fdied after being hit by a train in
OL,14,FMargam while working on the tracks
OL,15,Fbetween Port Talbot and Bridgend on 3
OL,16,FJuly 2019.
OL,18,FThey were part of a team carrying out
OL,19,Fmaintenance on the tracks.
