OL,6,FA report into the deaths of Gareth
OL,7,FDelbridge, 64, from Kenfig Hill and
OL,8,FMichael Lewis, 58, from North
OL,9,FCornelly, found an official lookout
OL,10,Fwas not in place on the day they died.
OL,12,FFriday's sentencing at Swansea Crown
OL,13,FCourt followed an investigation and
OL,14,Fprosecution by industry regulator the
OL,15,FOffice of Rail and Road (ORR).
OL,17,FNetwork Rail must pay the fines within
OL,18,F42 days, the court has ordered.
