OL,6,FFollowing the sentencing for a breach
OL,7,Fof the Health and Safety at Work Act
OL,8,F1974, Nick Millington, Route Director
OL,9,Fof Network Rail Wales & Borders, said:
OL,10,F"We know that the tragic deaths of our
OL,11,Fcolleagues, Gareth Delbridge and
OL,12,FMichael 'Spike' Lewis, should never
OL,13,Fhave happened on our railway and that
OL,14,Fhas been reflected by today's judgment.
OL,16,F"Over the last five years I have met
OL,17,Fregularly with Gareth and Spike's
OL,18,Ffamilies and our thoughts remain with
OL,19,Fthem, and all those friends and
OL,20,Fcolleagues who have been impacted by
OL,21,Ftheir deaths.
