OL,6,FNetwork Rail said it has already
OL,7,Fcommitted #70 million of investment to
OL,8,Ftrack worker safety initiatives, and
OL,9,Fhave invested a total of more than
OL,10,F#300 million to deliver an
OL,11,F"unprecedented" level of reform to
OL,12,Fworking practices.
OL,14,FRichard Hines, HM Chief Inspector of
OL,15,FRailways, said the fine "reflects the
OL,16,Fnature and gravity of Network Rail's
OL,17,Ffailings."
