OL,4,Cworker deaths
OL,6,FHe continued: "The rail industry needs
OL,7,Fto do all it practically can to help
OL,8,Feach worker get home safely every day.
OL,9,FMuch progress has been made in
OL,10,Freducing risk to track workers, with
OL,11,Fnew protections introduced.
OL,13,F"The industry is committed to seeing
OL,14,Fthese technologies implemented further
OL,15,Fand faster. This will require a
OL,16,Frelentless, collective, industry focus
OL,17,Fto continue to drive down risk to
OL,18,Fensure that tragic incidents such as
OL,19,Fthis are never repeated."
