OL,6,FIn a statement, The Rail Safety and
OL,7,FStandards Board's CEO, Mark Phillips
OL,8,Fsaid, "This tragic accident was a
OL,9,Fcatalyst to completely rethink track
OL,10,Fworker safety.
OL,12,F"Our research and analysis helped
OL,13,FNetwork Rail make significant safety
OL,14,Fimprovements, with our statistics
OL,15,Fshowing the number of track worker
OL,16,Fnear misses with trains reducing from
OL,17,F60 per year in 2018/19 to 22 in 2023/4.
