OL,6,F"This is still a priority issue for
OL,7,FRSSB, and we are developing new
OL,8,Fsolutions to protect track workers,
OL,9,Fincluding a predictive tool to reduce
OL,10,Fthe risk of runaway machinery,
OL,11,Fchanging standards to stop the highest
OL,12,Frisk activities and researching how
OL,13,Fgeofencing can improve safety at work
OL,14,Fsites, keeping staff within safe
OL,15,Fareas."
